Become the ultimate ninja and defeat deadly enemies!', 'NA', 34);

Offering a deep and original storyline that takes place during the Warring States Period of Japanese history alongside strategic sword-fighting action, Nioh will challenge players in a way that makes every mission and accomplishment feel earned and worthwhile.', 'NA', 34);

