The game consists of six short stages. It is an auto runner where prince must dodge traps and attack enemies. On the first stage, Prince only has time rewind power after death. The second stage introduces a boss battle where Prince has free movement. From the third stage onward the bosses can only be damaged by the elemental attacks. The elemental powers are different on each stage. The second stage Prince has also dash power. Third stage swaps the dash for freezing power. Fourth swaps the freeze for fire shield and attack. The fifth stage swaps from fire to earth shield. The final stage is a boss stage where Prince can freely swap between the four powers and only the matching color on the boss'' chest damages the boss', 'NA', 48);

