Far Cry 5
Welcome to Hope County, Montana. This idyllic place is home to a community of freedom-loving people - and a fanatical doomsday cult is known as The Project at Eden''s Gate. Led by the charismatic prophet Joseph Seed and his devoted siblings - The Heralds - Eden''s Gate has been quietly infiltrating every aspect of daily life in this once-quiet town. When your arrival incites the cult to violently seize control of the region, you must rise up and spark the fires of resistance to liberate a besieged community.

